                        Invitation to tender: Scheduled air services in Norway - 1 January 2008 – 31 March 2009
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[20.09.2007]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Transport and Communications invites tenders to an open tender procedure for regional scheduled air services on the routes Andenes – Bodø v.v. and Andenes – Tromsø v.v. during the period 1 January 2008 to 31 March 2009.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
