                <p>The Ministry of Transport and Communications now announces a vacant spectrum licence to operate a third generation public mobile communications system (3G). - I am pleased to facilitate for establishing a new mobile network and better infrastructure, says the Minister of Transport and Communications Liv Signe Navarsete.  (05.07.06)</p>
                
                
